title: Verify UCIDownloader handle UCI scores file with missing user_confidence_index in userid_riskscore_info
custom_summary: Verify UCIDownloader handle UCI scores file with missing user_confidence_index in userid_riskscore_info
custom_steps:
- Create a UCI score file with a incorrect format or value.
- Upload the modified UCI score file to the GCS bucket.
- Monitor UCIDownloader logs for any error or warning messages related to the file format or structure.
custom_expected:
- UCIDownloader should identify the incorrect file format or value.
- An error or warning message should be logged indicating that the uploaded file format or value is not supported.
